{"tid":2405700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄羅斯外長：若歐盟施加新制裁損害俄羅斯經濟，不排除與歐盟斷絕關係","createTime":"2021-02-12T14:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T07:20:53.000Z","uid":310867,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"76ffea57d4078697293b48212f8264b009ef13b8","tid":2405700,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫表示，如果歐盟將對俄羅斯施加的制裁，為經濟帶來風險，不排除與歐盟斷絕關係。<br />\n<br />\n拉夫羅夫對俄羅斯傳媒說，他們不想脫離世界生活，但是必須有所準備。如果想要和平，就要做好戰爭的準備。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">俄羅斯外交部上星期宣布，瑞典、波蘭和德國駐俄外交機構一些人員為不受歡迎人士，要求他們離境，因為他們參加未經官方批准，聲援反對派領袖納瓦爾尼的集會。</span><br />\n<br />\n莫斯科是在歐盟外交與安全政策高級代表博雷利訪問俄羅斯期間，驅逐歐洲三國外交官，博雷利認為，這說明俄羅斯不想抓住機會與歐盟展開建設性對話。歐盟必須制定方案，不排除追加制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575472-20210212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575472-20210212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=2e5446a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575472-20210212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=effa231e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575472-20210212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"82e12bf6c7287b449de1a027be083583856d7e01","tid":2405700,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"幾日前新聞：<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯說，有興趣恢復與歐盟的關係，但<span class=\"red\">反對歐盟干涉俄國內政。</span><br />\n<br />\n克里姆林宮發言人佩斯科夫說，俄羅斯不是俄歐關係轉差的始作俑者，強調雙方必須在<span class=\"red\">不干涉內政和尊重彼此利益的基礎上建立夥伴關係。</span><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯月初宣布驅逐瑞典、波蘭和德國外交人員出境，指他們<span class=\"red\">參加未經批准、聲援反對派領袖納瓦爾尼的集會。</span><br />\n<br />\n歐盟外交與安全政策高級代表博雷利早前訪問俄羅斯後表示，俄方在他訪俄期間驅逐歐洲外交官，說明莫斯科不想把握機會與歐盟展開建設性對話，歐盟必須制定方案要俄羅斯承擔後果，不排除實施進一步制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574822-20210209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574822-20210209.htm&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=1560af89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574822-20210209.htm&h=6391aa08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574822-20210209.htm</a>"},{"pid":"95e809828b605473009b5ac10f80201f7909a3f7","tid":2405700,"uid":143241,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"歐洲佬要天然氣定係要骨氣呢？"},{"pid":"2cc0a2a10169266babb1b54fe313c0552f6474e5","tid":2405700,"uid":34804,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"學埋中共果招<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似d仆街老豆咁，不停家暴打仔<br />\n同時用唔比家用/離婚黎威脅老婆唔好理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd8bed76e991d11d252d85bc803cc1a15b0db17","tid":2405700,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2cc0a2a10169266babb1b54fe313c0552f6474e5","tid":2405700,"uid":34804,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"學埋中共果招<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似d仆街老豆咁，不停家暴打仔<br />\n同時用唔比家用/離婚黎威脅老婆唔好理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"彼此彼此啦,邊有話邊個學邊個㗎！"},{"pid":"d0ffa4f33412bf6e70c796dcd210110838e13200","tid":2405700,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df126cab9189befbc8d15cc1fe82362ef7ad4f1","tid":2405700,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"斷啦屌<br />\nAll ta